field.value:
The RegisterErrorMessage() method is used to add error messages to an ErrorSummary instance. Instead of returning void, this method can return the ErrorSummary instance, allowing easier chaining of calls.

Examples from test case:

ErrorSummary summ1 = new ErrorSummary().RegisterErrorMessage("test1", "test1");
ErrorSummary summ2 = summ1.RegisterErrorMessage("test2", "test2").RegisterErrorMessage("test3", "test3");

This should be a no-impact change. Patch file will be attached.
